Class ClipboardWatcherService

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.content.Context

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.content.ClipboardManager.OnPrimaryClipChangedListener, android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.content.ComponentCallbacks2

    public class ClipboardWatcherService
extends android.app.Service
implements android.content.ClipboardManager.OnPrimaryClipChangedListener
    An app private Service to listen for changes to the clipboard, persist them to storage using ClipsContentProvider and push them to registered FCM devices
